name: Z DishWasher Corp. 13 year Moving Avg. (CHR#4)
description:
JaZoN Ex.* Data Charts. Representing life value in the long term.

* JaZoN Ex. redefines portraiture, self worth, and the value of an individual in the form of a stock market. Composed of companies that valorize living in all its forms: experiences, intellect, sexuality, physical health, emotions… etc, the oeuvre is a multi faceted, continually evolving accumulation and implementation of data generated by JaZoN’s interpretation of life. Featuring hundreds of thousands of price evaluations to date, the global project is expressed in both virtual and physical forms going all the way back to 2007.

www.jazonex.com

part of ZEconomy ecosystem.
